OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northeast.
OL,8,FThe rain will be mostly light and
OL,9,Fpatchy, but perhaps heavier for a time
OL,10,Fthis evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny early morning rain will
OL,13,Fquickly clear away. Otherwise a bright
OL,14,Fday with sunny spells and a few
OL,15,Fscattered showers, one or two on the
OL,16,Fheavy side in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
